snippet.title: Happy's Humble Burger Farm | Coming to Steam, PlayStation, Xbox on December 3 | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Happy’s Humble Burger Farm, a first person adventure horror cooking game, is coming to PlayStation, Xbox, Switch this year. Tune in for a date announcement for a new gameplay trailer reveal! Don't forget to press "Set Reminder"

Wishlist and follow on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1433340/Happys_Humble_Burger_Farm/

https://www.happyshumble.com/

#PS4 #Switch #Xbox
